1. *Ogromnu* tortu smo kupili za slavlje. (We bought a *huge* cake for the celebration.)
2. Za ovaj posao će ti biti potrebna *ogromna* količina vremena. (You will need a *tremendous* amount of time for this job.)
3. Mislila sam da će mi biti teško, ali sam ipak pretrčala *ogromnu* razdaljinu. (I thought it would be hard, but I still ran a *huge* distance.)
4. *Ogromnu* kuću su izgradili na brdu iznad grada. (They built a *gigantic* house on the hill above the city.)
5. Moramo pronaći način da smanjimo *ogromne* troškove. (We need to find a way to reduce *enormous* expenses.)
6. Nije mi se svidela ta haljina zbog *ogromnog* uzorka. (I didn't like that dress because of the *huge* pattern.)
7. Dok sam vozio auto, na putu sam vidio *ogromnu* količinu snijega. (While driving the car, I saw a *massive* amount of snow on the road.)
8. Saznao sam da je moja baka naslijedila *ogromnu* količinu novca. (I found out that my grandmother inherited a *huge* amount of money.)
9. U gradu je izgrađena *ogromna* zgrada, koja je postala simbol grada. (A *huge* building was constructed in the city, which became a symbol of the city.)
10. *Ogromni* talasi su udarali o obalu, a vjetar je bio vrlo jak. (The *giant* waves were crashing against the shore, and the wind was very strong.)